What you need to know:

Gareth Bale's corner arrowed towards Lucas at the near post and the Brazilian edged in front of his marker to glance a header past Lukasz Fabianski.Bale almost equalised with a blistering effort from the edge of the area that cannoned off the bar.Tottenham's luck was out again in stoppage-time when the ball rebounded off Son but looped onto the post and bounced to safety.